video.title: Power Rangers Lost Galaxy
video.synopsis: Five teenagers, transformed by the mystical powers of the Quasar Sabers into the Galaxy Power Rangers, battle the evil Scorpius and Captain Mutiny.

episodes.synopsis: An adventurous young man embarks on an epic adventure in space when he sneaks aboard the massive space colony Terra Venture.
episodes.title: Quasar Quest: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Galaxy Rangers are born as five heroes unite to protect the planet Mirinoi from the villain Furio.
episodes.title: Quasar Quest: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers befriend the Galactabeasts -- five enormous animals that help them defend Terra Venture against the forces of the evil Scorpius.
episodes.title: Race to the Rescue

episodes.synopsis: Leo adjusts to his responsibilities as a member of the GSA when he forgets to properly lock a weapon storage room on Terra Venture.
episodes.title: Rookie in Red

episodes.synopsis: A homesick boy who misses Earth helps the Rangers during Furio's sleeping-gas attack on Terra Venture.
episodes.title: Homesick

episodes.synopsis: The shape-changing monster Mutantrum poses as Mike to lure Leo to the legendary Lights of Orion.
episodes.title: The Lights of Orion

episodes.synopsis: Battling the Wisewizard, Kendrix meets an actress on a movie set who looks exactly like her.
episodes.title: Double Duty

episodes.synopsis: Kai is smitten by a pretty girl but has little time for romance as the Quake Maker monster attacks Terra Venture with earthquakes.
episodes.title: The Blue Crush

episodes.synopsis: The heroic Magna Defender renews his feud with Scorpius's new general, Treacheron.
episodes.title: The Magna Defender

episodes.synopsis: Seeking vengeance for his son, the Magna Defender battles the Fish Face monster on Terra Venture.
episodes.title: Sunflower Search

episodes.synopsis: Leo and the Magna Defender are forced to work together when the Chillyfish monster freezes the people of Terra Venture.
episodes.title: Silent Sleep

episodes.synopsis: Kendrix and Maya work to escape from a force field created by the monster Destruxo before he can find the Lights of Orion.
episodes.title: Orion Rising

episodes.synopsis: It's a three-way race between the Power Rangers, the Magna Defender and Destruxo as the Lights of Orion return.
episodes.title: Orion Returns

episodes.synopsis: Treacheron turns on Trakeena as the Power Rangers must fight the Shark Brothers without Leo.
episodes.title: Shark Attack

episodes.synopsis: The Magna Defender struggles to overcome his regrets of the past while protecting Terra Venture.
episodes.title: Redemption Day

episodes.synopsis: Mike returns to Terra Venture and searches for a new role to fight against the Skelekron monster.
episodes.title: Destined for Greatness

episodes.synopsis: Trakeena worries about losing her beauty when her father, Scorpius, wants her to become a full insect like him.
episodes.title: Stolen Beauty

episodes.synopsis: Commander Stanton sends a boarding party to investigate a derelict spaceship with a dangerous secret.
episodes.title: The Rescue Mission

episodes.synopsis: The treacherous Deviot assists Scorpius by unleashing three lost Galactabeasts to attack Terra Venture.
episodes.title: The Lost Galactabeasts: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers struggle to free the lost Galactabeasts from Deviot.
episodes.title: The Lost Galactabeasts: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: While Trakeena makes new allies on Onyx, Deviot plots against Scorpius.
episodes.title: Heir to the Throne

episodes.synopsis: Seeking vengeance, Trakeena captures Leo while Deviot plots against her.
episodes.title: An Evil Game

episodes.synopsis: Maya's best friend from her home world, Shondra, arrives on Terra Venture, but Kendrix suspects Shondra may not be who she claims.
episodes.title: Memories of Mirinoi

episodes.synopsis: Trakeena blackmails Terra Venture into sending their best engineer to repair the Scorpion Stinger's engines.
episodes.title: Green Courage

episodes.synopsis: Kai suspects Commander Stanton is under mind control when he orders Terra Venture steered into the course of a nearby star.
episodes.title: Blue to the Test

episodes.synopsis: Leo, Damon and Kai race the Motor Mantis monster on motorcycles. The prize: Kendrix and Maya!
episodes.title: Mean Wheels Mantis

episodes.synopsis: Deviot sends the honorable warrior Loyax to destroy the Rangers, but when he meets Maya, he questions the honor in his ways.
episodes.title: Loyax' Last Battle

episodes.synopsis: Leo struggles to earn the approval of the brother of the girl he wants to date while trying to save her from Trakeena's latest monster.
episodes.title: A Red Romance

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers fight the Chameliac Warrior to save their Galactabeasts.
episodes.title: The Chameliac Warrior

episodes.synopsis: Deviot enlists the Psycho Rangers to capture the Galaxy Rangers, prompting Andros and the Space Rangers to travel to Terra Venture to help.
episodes.title: To the 10th Power

episodes.synopsis: The Space Rangers and Galaxy Rangers unite to help Kendrix against the Pink Psycho Ranger.
episodes.title: The Power of Pink

episodes.synopsis: Karone once again assumes the role of Astronema as she risks her life to save the Pink Quasar Saber from falling into the hands of evil.
episodes.title: Protect the Quasar Saber

episodes.synopsis: Karone struggles to overcome her evil past as Astronema while adjusting to being the new Pink Galaxy Ranger.
episodes.title: Facing the Past

episodes.synopsis: Damon competes against an unscrupulous rival for the position of head mechanic on Terra Venture.
episodes.title: Turn Up the Volume

episodes.synopsis: The Terra Venture discovers the fabled Lost Galaxy.
episodes.title: Enter the Lost Galaxy

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers are welcomed to the Lost Galaxy by a scheming space pirate named Captain Mutiny.
episodes.title: Beware the Mutiny

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers battle the enormous Grunchor monster that has burrowed inside Terra Venture.
episodes.title: Grunchor On the Loose

episodes.synopsis: Captured by Deviot, Leo and Damon reminisce over their adventures up until now.
episodes.title: Until Sunset

episodes.synopsis: Captain Mutiny's sorceress, Hexuba, uses her magic to cause the Power Rangers to fall into a deep, restless sleep.
episodes.title: Dream Battle

episodes.synopsis: Hexuba uses her magic to resurrect defeated monsters to battle the Power Rangers.
episodes.title: Hexuba's Graveyard

episodes.synopsis: Captain Mutiny unleashes the gargantuan Titanisaur on Terra Venture, the greatest threat the Rangers have faced yet.
episodes.title: Raise the Titanisaur

episodes.synopsis: Mike makes a sacrifice to help Terra Venture escape the Lost Galaxy.
episodes.title: Escape the Lost Galaxy

episodes.synopsis: Terra Venture discovers a lush green planet to colonize as Trakeena merges with Deviot to become stronger than ever.
episodes.title: Journey's End: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers work to evacuate the crew of Terra Venture as Trakeena launches her final assault.
episodes.title: Journey's End: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Trapped on a desolate moon in the ruins of Terra Venture, Leo faces Trakeena all alone.
episodes.title: Journey's End: Part 3
